values: so i have not written in here in awhile so i just thought i would say hey! i am really havin fun up here in starkvegas except i am poor!  i mean i have a job at kroger but i only get like 16 hours a week like every other cashier so i need to find another job with more money! i mean i am supposed to be getting an apartment with kyle but i have no freakin clue how that is goin to pan out! i just got back from my chem II lab for 3 fucking hours and, of course, me and my partner are the only ones that had problems!! so that will promise to be a bad lab grade!! i am going home next weekend for my birthday!!!! hopefully that will be fun!! but i am gonna go study for my chem test so i will say hey again when i am out of hell!! later

so i havent really written in here in a month but now i am in starkville i just got up here thursday and got in my dorm.  it is pretty cool but different i will have to get used to it.  i start my new job tomorrow at kroger which to my surprise is not much different than winn dixie.  it was really easy getting the job though that is all that counts. well that is all for now.

omg i am done with my final english paper and my western civ paper and it is only 1:00 am on sunday night!!! one is 10 pages and the other is 8 pages i feel so accomplished!! and tomorrow is also my last real day of classes until exams so that is pretty awesome!! kyle is comin down tomorrow and we are gonna have so much fun !! also me and my mom went and got our christmas tree last night and we got a 9 1/2 foot tree for $40 which is really good then the tree people asked us for some beer so we brought them a six pack which was pretttty interesting but anyways i am gonna go to bed now because i cannot wait til tomorrow!!!!!! like totalLY!!!!!!!! later

so it is now 3:19 am and it is like the latest i have been up in a very long time. The reason for this madness is stupid fucking english2 and i am having to write my final research paper by monday and i havent even started!!!!!!!!!! i am so horrible usually i have it done like at least 5 days before but noooo.  of course it is not totally my fault because my mom dragged me around town all day and night today but uh well.  so this sucks because i took a stacker earlier to try and stay up and it made me fall asleep on and off like 3 hours ago but now im up and reaady to go but i cant i have to go to sleep or i will  never last tomorrow!!! so i am gonna go try that and see how it works out it will be like my 3rd attempt to go to bed for the night but ya know it happens! see ya later !

well guys thanks for the welcoming haha thanks to kyle!  so i kinda am getting used to this thing because i talk about all my problems yeah thats right like all 30 of them but thats okay because i only have two more days of regular class left over at usa!!! thank god!!!  then of course i have exams but at least i will not have to go there anymore because me no like! so i think me and my mom are going to go get a christmas tree this weekend with waht money i do not know but we will somehow get one and tomorrow i have to go to my little niece's bday party what fun !! then of course is my english paper that i never started on i guess that project will consume my entire day off saturday i guess i will just drink while i do it so it wont be so bad. haha joke guys i cant write a paper wasted i mean i dont think?! but anyways im gonna go crash because i am feeling pretty freakin tired so i will talk to everyone later !!

so kyle just made me my own livejournal and made it alllll about him which is totally cool.  let me tell you we had so much fun over the thanksgiving break at kyle's dads except for the wreck that is and that i have to find $500 in like 3 weeks but thats okay i will live i promise.  i really do not know what i am supposed to talk about on these things but uh well. i do know that i cannot wait til next week when kyle comes down and we all get to hang out with no school and all that. then after that no more usa and i will be heading to state and most likely rooming with sierra battle.  haha i am sure that is going to be an interesting first semester away from home and i am soooo excited.  for now though i am going to go work on my final paper for comp2. yeay!!! what fun see ya later
